high_descs: Turn around and head towards the stove.
Pick up the egg behind the bowl next to the stove.
Turn right and head towards the sink.
Wash the egg in the sink and pick it back up.
Turn left to face the microwave.
Place the egg on the blue plate in the microwave and close it.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed egg in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around, proceed to counter and stove.
Pick up egg from behind bowl.
Put egg in right side of sink, fill and empty sink, remove egg from sink.
Open microwave, put egg in across from mug, shut microwave.
anns.task_desc: Clean egg in sink then put in microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and move across the room to the stove.
Pick up the egg sitting to the right of the soap bottle and left of the stove.
Turn right and move to the sink.
Wash the egg in the sink.
Put the egg in the microwave on the left side of the plate.
anns.task_desc: Cook a clean egg in the microwave.
